      "title": "My latest books cartoon for The Guardian&rsquo;s books pages.",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s640x960/9a73f78dd1b9e0b2bb07eeadd08af6d8e30ab5d4.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"832\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Panel 1&#10;A small girl and boy are reading on the floor. A father appears at the door and says:&#10;&quot;This is so nice to see! I heard that kids these days weren't reading.&quot; &#10;One of the children says &quot;Ugh, reading? So lame!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 2&#10;She continues &quot;It's called Booksmaxxing now, Dad!&quot;&#10;He replies as he is leaving &quot;'m just happy you're enjoying it.&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 3&#10;The boy says &quot;Booksmaxxing?&quot;&#10;The girl says &quot;I like to mess with him.&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s75x75_c1/4ccf031001b120b447700c14a4ded863669abea4.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s100x200/5cdafa5bdae44f258baad8d3905e7ed11ae3fe0b.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s250x400/c3315794767682447b0fc7413c54c933384fd553.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s400x600/1cbb1fc88eb2918fac3b8d9212ee68d8222cd8d7.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s500x750/ac45341aa32ec29ac1b97e9f4ba9102a6ff38a89.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s540x810/d751ae348c3b2616c07a8573f5d68ab9e07acd45.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s640x960/9a73f78dd1b9e0b2bb07eeadd08af6d8e30ab5d4.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s1280x1920/8b684ce0645ec62f395012c3390eda9f1b201406.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/06c76cf2451eac4216b75026933420ca/60d6a01bd3e5a5dd-16/s2048x3072/bd12164462a8b02