    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/816960304513695744",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/816960304513695744",
      "title": "My latest cartoon for Guardian Books",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/3348c5a42083bcb582fd095727a49f98/8ccd0051d376d084-3e/s640x960/74d8d4e6c4eaac4b76223f0c4e754d1ca033afb0.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"818\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Panel 1&#10;Caption: 2025, Middlemarch Is voted the best novel of all time and wins the right to represent earth at the IGCLC* finals. &#10;Image: The cover of George Eliot's 'Middlemarch'&#10;*Intergalactic literary Champions league &#10;&#10;&#10;Panel 2&#10;Caption: 2028, A young Editor from Penguin Classics climbs Aboard Artemis VII for the thirty-year journey to host planet, Kepler-22b. She carries a first Edition of the book in a lead-lined briefcase. &#10;Image: Astronaut boarding enormous spaceship.&#10;&#10;Panel 3&#10;Caption: 2089, She returns with news that earth placed a very respectable third, and that she bought rights to the two winning novels.&#10;Images: The capsule returns to earth and splashes down in the sea. The astronaut emerges and waves to the rescue helicopter.&#10;&#10;Panel 4&#10;Caption: 2092, The alien books are translated and published to critical acclaim and modest sales. &#10;Image: Two books. 'Magnesium Sunset' by Zylob Pyrxx and 'Orbital Amnesia' by Unaha Closp &#10;More caption: Middlemarch is a runaway success in gas-form on Proxima Centauri b.&#10;Final image: An alien happily reading a small cloud.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/3348c5a42083bcb582fd095727a49f98/8ccd0051d376d084-3e/s75x75_c1/b2297d1f84eef5bf57e711f2ed46e83972b1d69b.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3348c5a42083bcb582fd095727a49f98/8ccd0051d376d084-3e/s100x200/0f8decb19ebdc956685399bd72150166a8b65e33.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3348c5a42083bcb582fd095727a49f98/8ccd0051d376d084-3e/s250x400/cdfbef97264feeeeaf186c3c6f056e073bfd28f1.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3348c5a42083bcb582fd095727a49f98/8ccd0051d376d084-3e/s400x600/07ccfb4f3d6b8fe80b05f6025d3599d9882fcb66.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/3348c5a42083bcb